videos.headline: Pitt strikes first vs. UNC with rushing TD
videos.description: Vincent Davis punches it in for Pitt as the Panthers take a 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt strikes first vs. UNC with rushing TD) 2021/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pickett finds Bartholomew for the short passing TD
videos.description: Kenny Pickett has Pitt up 14-0 with this quick strike to Gavin Bartholomew.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pickett finds Bartholomew for the short passing TD) 2021/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell finds Antoine Green for the 76-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Howell goes deep to a wide-open Antoine Green to cut into the Panthers' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell finds Antoine Green for the 76-yard TD) 2021/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell connects with Green for another TD
videos.description: Sam Howell finds Antoine Green again in the end zone to cut into the Panthers' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell connects with Green for another TD ) 2021/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Downs lays out for a 50-yard reception from Howell
videos.description: Carolina is set up in the red zone after this diving catch from Josh Downs.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Downs lays out for a 50-yard reception from Howell) 2021/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt strikes first in OT
videos.description: Kenny Picket throws the TD pass to Lucas Kroll to take the lead in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt strikes first in OT) 2021/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt seals OT win by picking off Howell
videos.description: Sam Howell gets picked off as Pitt seals a 30-23 win over North Carolina in overtime.

videos.headline: Pitt fends off furious comeback from UNC
videos.description: UNC fights back from a 16-point deficit in the second half but falls short in overtime.
